Auguste Bartholdi presented three models before his project was accepted. Ferdinand Barbedienne, a French industrialist, took charge of the foundry work. Built in 1873, this bronze statue celebrates a local child, Marshal S√©bastien Le Prestre, Marquis de Vauban. The castle of Bazoche, the latter's residence, is located nearby; its visit will satisfy the most demanding visitors.  Vauban was an exceptional military architect, who, promoted by Louis XIV, marked his era with gigantic construction sites for fortified places. But he was a creator of genius with boundless activity in many fields, town planning, hydraulics. He was also a French thinker and essayist.
